ap. Each snapshot","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","isActive":true},{"text":" object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","isActive":true},{"text":" object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"asynchronously, calling ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","isActive":true},{"text":" methods if defined, then","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the snapshot are finished loading.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","abstract":[{"text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshot","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshot"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is an abstract superclass used to define shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"composed of multiple vertices."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMultiPoint","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPoint","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"title":"MLNMultiPolyline","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"}}}